item.title: Sleep
item.dc:creator: @gothic_queen casey.
item.description:
@gothic_queen wrote:

zyle1992:

If it’s only 3 hours, stay up, and grab some energy drinks/shots/coffee on your way to school. Sleeping now would only do more damage.

Nah.

IIRC from one of my psych classes, you’ll go throw a REM cycle in that amount of time. If he’s going to school, the short amount of sleep will at least improve his comprehension and concentration. I don’t recommend the consumption of any energy drinks, but if you choose to do so do it at mid day so at least you can crash for a bit when your home(but only nap for a short amount of time so you don’t create a cycle)
